The paper discusses a method for improving the performance of neural networks in scenarios where most class labels are rare, such as language modelling. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the sub-categories of machine learning (cs.LG), natural language processing (cs.CL), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), computer vision (cs.CV), and neural and evolutionary computing (cs.NE).
